## Best Practices

### 1. Logging Centralizzato

```javascript
const { getLogger } = require("./logging");
const logger = getLogger("provider-name", "service");

// Uso consistente del logging
logger.info(`Processing request for user ${userId}`);
logger.warn(`Fallback to local storage: ${error.message}`);
logger.error(`API call failed: ${error.message}`);
```

### 2. Gestione Cache

```javascript
const getAvailableModels = async () => {
	if (
		AVAILABLE_MODELS.length > 0 &&
		lastModelsFetch &&
		Date.now() - lastModelsFetch < CACHE_DURATION
	) {
		return AVAILABLE_MODELS;
	}

	const models = await fetchAvailableModels();
	AVAILABLE_MODELS = models;
	lastModelsFetch = Date.now();
	return models;
};
```

### 3. Timeout e Retry

```javascript
// Per chiamate API esterne
const response = await axios.post(API_URL, payload, {
	headers: { "Api-Key": config.provider.apiKey },
	timeout: 30000,
	maxContentLength: 20 * 1024 * 1024,
});

// Per download immagini
let attempts = 0;
const maxAttempts = 3;
while (attempts < maxAttempts) {
	try {
		// Operazione
		break;
	} catch (error) {
		attempts++;
		if (attempts >= maxAttempts) throw error;
		await new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, 1000 * attempts));
	}
}
```

